column2: select top # s.*, g.* from (select top # * from samples order by newid () ) s cross join (select top # * from genes order by newid () ) g) select bw.sampleId, bw.chr, bl.* from sg inner join bw on bw.sampleid = sg.sampleid and bw.chr = sg.chr and bw.lo < = sg.endLoc and bw.hi > = sg.startLoc cross apply dbo.fGetBlocksWigTable (block, sg.startLoc, sg.endLoc) bl order by bw.sampleid, bw.chr, bl.lo
